text: Laila Soufyane (born 4 August 1983) is a born Moroccan Italian female long- distance runner, who won two Italian championships. ==National titles== * Italian Athletics Championships ** 10 km road: 2014 ** Half marathon: 2015 ==See also== * Naturalized athletes of Italy ==References== ==External links== * * Laila Soufyane at FIDAL Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Italian female long-distance runners Category:Moroccan emigrants to Italy Category:Naturalised citizens of Italy Category:Italian female marathon runners Category:Athletics competitors of Gruppo Sportivo Esercito
